  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Reversing Margin Flows</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio8715da531198434de10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Reversing Margin Flows </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> You use this transaction to reverse postings for variation margins and close margins that are incorrect.\n</p>\n<aside class=\"note\" aria-labelledby=\"n0t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n0t\"><strong>Note</strong></div>\n<ul class=\"ul\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> After you have reversed the variation margin, the corresponding flows are removed.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> When reversing close margin flows, the system generates new flows with <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">planned</span> status.\n</p></li></ul></aside>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Procedure\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Procedure</h2>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">On the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">SAP Easy Access</span> screen, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Treasury and Risk Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transaction Manager</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Derivatives</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Accounting</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Posting</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Margin Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Reverse Margin Flows</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> (PMSV).\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Enter the company code, futures account, ID number, and the reversal reason.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose the key date from when all margin flows are to be reversed.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Test Run</span> indicator if you only want to simulate database changes.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute</span> .\n</p></li></ol>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}